    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you should expect some minor oil seepage and a suspension that feels a bit loose over bumps. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some fading in the clear coat, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and a few non-functional plastic trim pieces. It is a solid candidate for someone looking for a budget-friendly vehicle who doesn't mind doing some light maintenance and cosmetic touch-ups.",
