      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as-is. While it remains a functional daily driver, the exterior shows noticeable wear including several scratches and some fading paint, and the interior has visible signs of use. It is mechanically sound for now, but a potential buyer should expect some upcoming maintenance to keep it running reliably. It\u2019s a solid, budget-friendly option for someone looking for basic transportation.",
