    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This unit represents the pinnacle of its class, boasting an unblemished exterior and a cabin that retains its original showroom luster. Mechanically superior and aesthetically flawless, it offers an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning collector. Every detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our rigorous criteria for excellence, representing a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of this caliber.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
